message.subject: Sprint planning
message.body:
Hello there, I wanted to take a moment to properly introduce myself. My name is Kayla, and I will be taking over as the primary point of contact for this project moving forward, following the recent departmental reorganization. I've spent the past few days getting up to speed on all the documentation and previous correspondence, and I'm really excited to dive in and start collaborating with you. I'll be reaching out again very shortly to schedule a more formal introductory meeting where we can discuss the next steps and align on our goals for the coming quarter. I'm truly looking forward to a productive and successful partnership.

Warmly,
Kayla
